# Home Assistant — UI + API.
# HA runs network_mode: host in the Colima VM, listening on :8123.
# Reach via the VM's vmnet IP from the Mac (Caddy proxies through).
# Both `homeassistant.int` (HA's own preferred spelling) and the
# hyphenated `home-assistant.int` resolve; pick whichever feels natural.
homeassistant.int, home-assistant.int {
    import homelab_tls
    reverse_proxy 192.168.64.2:8123
}
